data.description: Motivated sellers- offering $2500 in buyer incentives to be used for a rate buydown or decorator allowance as you see fit (with an acceptable offer). Come check out this super cute house located in desirable Floresville. A short commute to San Antonio makes this an ideal location. This home has been updated and well taken care of. Enjoy late evenings relaxing on the golf course and enjoying a meal at their on site restaurant. You don't won't want to miss this one!!
